# Gym Management API - Tests Collection
# Documentation: https://localhost:7114/swagger

### Variables d'environnement
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7114
@authApiUrl = https://localhost:7203
@authToken = {{auth_token}}
@userId = 1
@clubId = 1
@membershipPlanId = 1

### ======================
### AUTHENTIFICATION
### ======================

### Obtenir un token d'authentification
POST {{authApiUrl}}/api/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@gym.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### ======================
### USERS - ADMIN ROUTES
### ======================

### Créer un utilisateur (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John",
    "surname": "Doe",
    "birthdate": "1990-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "password": "SecurePass123!",
    "role": 1,
    "email": "john.doe@email.com",
    "phoneNumber": "0123456789",
    "gender": 1,
    "country": 1,
    "city": "Paris",
    "street": "123 Main St",
    "postalCode": "75001",
    "number": "42"
}

### Obtenir un utilisateur par ID (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Obtenir tous les utilisateurs (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?page-size=10&page-number=1&email=
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Modifier un utilisateur (Admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Updated",
    "email": "john.updated@email.com",
    "role": 2
}

### Supprimer un utilisateur (Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ======================
### USERS - APP ROUTES
### ======================

### Modifier son propre profil (App)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/app/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Self-Updated",
    "email": "john.self@email.com"
}

### Obtenir son profil (App)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/app/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ======================
### CLUBS - ADMIN ROUTES
### ======================

### Créer un club (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/clubs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Fitness Plus",
    "description": "Club de fitness moderne",
    "country": 1,
    "city": "Lyon",
    "street": "456 Gym Ave",
    "postalCode": "69001",
    "number": "10"
}

### Obtenir tous les clubs (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/clubs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Obtenir un club par ID (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/clubs/{{clubId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Modifier un club (Admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/clubs/{{clubId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Fitness Plus Updated",
    "description": "Club de fitness moderne et équipé"
}

### ======================
### MEMBERSHIP PLANS - ADMIN ROUTES
### ======================

### Créer un plan d'abonnement (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/membership-plans
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "Plan Premium",
    "basePrice": 49.99,
    "membershipPlanType": 1,
    "yearlyDiscount": 10.0,
    "registrationFees": 20.0
}

### Obtenir tous les plans d'abonnement (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/membership-plans
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Obtenir un plan d'abonnement par ID (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/membership-plans/{{membershipPlanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Modifier un plan d'abonnement (Admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/membership-plans/{{membershipPlanId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "Plan Premium Updated",
    "basePrice": 54.99,
    "yearlyDiscount": 15.0
}

### ======================
### SOUSCRIPTIONS - ADMIN ROUTES
### ======================

### Souscrire un utilisateur à un plan (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}/subscribe
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "membershipPlanId": {{membershipPlanId}},
    "clubId": {{clubId}},
    "membershipPeriod": 1
}

### Effectuer un paiement (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/{{userId}}/memberships/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 49.99,
    "paymentMethod": 1
}

### ======================
### QR CODES - APP ROUTES
### ======================

### Générer un QR code (App)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/app/users/{{userId}}/qr-code
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "clubId": {{clubId}}
}

### Valider un QR code (App)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/app/users/validate-qr-code
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "qrCodePayload": "generated-qr-code-payload"
}